latestIgtvVideos.caption:
~ Jasmine ~

What if your wedding lehenga narrated your love story? 
Yes! My haldi lehenga depicted my love for silver jewellery to a level that my entire ensemble was made from tiny silver motifs like bird, lotus, fish, butterflies, rose etc.

Until now, lehengas were just outfits. But for me, it went far beyond just style. This is now the piece of artwork that unfolds not just my persona, but my memories and meaningful experiences with my work.

The Chandi Studio has been a beautiful & the most hard working journey for me & I thought of translating this milestone onto one of my wedding outfit.

Watching this piece come to life felt like a therapy session.

It was worth all the effort & pain because the end product had everyone captivated. 

And today my lehenga not just sits in my closet, but stands as a special piece of artwork and beautiful memoir 💛

Would love love love to hear your feedback! :)

Outfit : @krishfashionjaipur 
Jewellery : @the_chandi_studio

latestIgtvVideos.title: Creating the life of my dreams ✨
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Safar, The Chandi Studio ka! ♥️

16 February, 2018. First dispatch from The Chandi Studio 🙏🏻

From old cardboard box, 2 team members, unnamed packaging to heritage cardboard box, 7 team members & our lovely packaging! 

Everything changed. What remained the same was unconditional effort, care & always a happy face while packaging every product at The Chandi Studio.

I owe it all to only God, my family, friends, team & of course you all lovely beautiful fantastic clients ✨

Love you all with all my heart. 
Brb. Crying 😭♥️

Ps : Edited the number of followers in poem because there was a significant change in them after lockdown 😄

#myheartissofull
